<h2><a class="listing" style="article" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/International-Women-s-Day-2011-Women-Farmers-Voiceless-Pillars-of-African-Agriculture" title="International Women's Day 2011 | &quot;Women Farmers: Voiceless Pillars of African Agriculture&quot;" alt="article">International Women's Day 2011 | &quot;Women Farmers: Voiceless Pillars of African Agriculture&quot;</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
