<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Institutional-Learning-and-Change-ILAC-Initiative-Feb.-2011-Updates" title="Institutional Learning and Change (ILAC) Initiative – Feb. 2011 Updates" alt="link">Institutional Learning and Change (ILAC) Initiative – Feb. 2011 Updates</a></h2>

	
